# --- IMPORTANT NOTE ON LOCK FILES ---
# Files like package-lock.json (npm), yarn.lock (Yarn), pnpm-lock.yaml (pnpm),
# Cargo.lock (Rust), Pipfile.lock (pipenv), poetry.lock (Poetry)
# are generally RECOMMENDED to be committed to your repository.
# They ensure that everyone on the team and your CI/CD systems
# get the exact same versions of dependencies, leading to reproducible builds.
# Only ignore them if you have a very specific reason.
